1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:56:44.000Z","msg":"珍 悶到"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:58:24.000Z","msg":"圍爐"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:59:01.000Z","msg":"人少到圍唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T05:59:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5630466c69a58d3b7aa85194f7fc144dd749a6fd","tid":1911774,"uid":170176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"冇方向嘅時候都真係會有啲迷失嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲野又迫唔黎<br />\n對住一啲自己唔中意嘅人<br />\n正常人都唔會有太多恒心嘅<br />\n<br />\n巴打你平時有啲咩興趣阿？"},{"pid":"c074f769ee770f79bf5487f5dd8264dbcce10b9d","tid":1911774,"uid":35484,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T21:16:47.000Z","msg":"諸事不順皆因不孝，諸事不順皆因犯邪淫<br />\n<br />\n只要犯以上兩種，你既運氣，人生，福報就會不斷下降，這是千真萬確既事實<br />\n想要人生變得更好，第一孝順，第二戒邪淫，（包括打丁，叫雞，一夜情等等），第三行善積德<br />\n只要照住上面３樣去做好一年，你會慢慢發覺自己既人生越黎越好。<br />\n<br />\n可睇秦東魁老師講既ＹＯＵＴＵＢＥ視頻<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fchannel%2FUCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA&d=%2BwrRK7ySmiC6A5TqlPyaq6DCEJE6krTJKQ6%2BfiBCJRk%3D&h=4f8aa389\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCGbqgMSR8XSVQ5GZJRgNcMA</a>"},{"pid":"b0e6465f8a01ae3880d28556743a3631a3968438","tid":1911774,"uid":251581,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8552360fd1a73e394b040563b06800c808ed4e47","tid":1911774,"uid":314145,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-03-05T14:43:18.000Z","msg":"有冇人覺得自己好冇用 <br />\n成20歲人一事無成<br />\n冇毅力 冇恆心<br />\n全部野都堅持唔耐<br />\n書又讀唔好<br />\n一啲用都冇<br />\n成日覺得屋企人對自己咁好好浪費佢地心機<br />\n完全唔值得<br />\n死左又好對唔住屋企人咁多年黎既照顧<br />\n唉<br />\n應該點先可以搵到人生目標同埋價值"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T21:28:13.000Z","msg":"你睇下鄺俊宇既故事，就會好好多。<br />\n因為大家都係學業唔好，對自己有懷疑，迷失過。<br />\n其實我都係，我都垃圾過兩三年。<br />\n其實廢青一下真係冇咩大不了，睇下書先囉，<br />\n諗下自己想做乜。<br />\n打下機開心下先。<br />\n但係生活都要控制好唔好成日夜訓，飲酒。<br />\n咁慢慢等自己舒緩下先。"},{"pid":"203950cc8a4740d4b10db580bc97e22c3e63e40c","tid":1911774,"uid":99930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T22:42:20.000Z","msg":"做唔到政府工，冇資格拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b1e8313c0f67c54bd3ea01d08bc591412ce1e4b1","tid":1911774,"uid":314145,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5630466c69a58d3b7aa85194f7fc144dd749a6fd","tid":1911774,"uid":170176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"冇方向嘅時候都真係會有啲迷失嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲野又迫唔黎<br />\n對住一啲自己唔中意嘅人<br />\n正常人都唔會有太多恒心嘅<br />\n<br />\n巴打你平時有啲咩興趣阿？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T04:39:46.000Z","msg":"毒L 平時同朋友打下機<br />\n自己睇下書 玩下模型咁 <br />\n自己又內向 新環境基本冇新朋友"},{"pid":"8127f770c911648c9aee02ef576203c6e62884fe","tid":1911774,"uid":170176,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b1e8313c0f67c54bd3ea01d08bc591412ce1e4b1","tid":1911774,"uid":314145,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"5630466c69a58d3b7aa85194f7fc144dd749a6fd","tid":1911774,"uid":170176,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-10T07:54:51.000Z","msg":"冇方向嘅時候都真係會有啲迷失嘅<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有啲野又迫唔黎<br />\n對住一啲自己唔中意嘅人<br />\n正常人都唔會有太多恒心嘅<br />\n<br />\n巴打你平時有啲咩興趣阿？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T04:39:46.000Z","msg":"毒L 平時同朋友打下機<br />\n自己睇下書 玩下模型咁 <br />\n自己又內向 新環境基本冇新朋友"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-03-11T05:44:04.000Z","msg":"屋企人對自己好係因為大家血濃於水<img src=\"/asset